abstract_summ: 2019-nCoV confirmed group (n=35) had fewer fever (OR[95% CI] 0.39[0.242 to 0.628];P<.001) and symptoms of ARI (0.454) More asymptomatic (15.086[2117 to 107.475]), and more family cluster infections (5.469[2405 to 12.433]); chest CT had more positive findings of viral pneumonia (1.813[1.131 to 2.908];P=.014)
